xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml"><fr:frontmatter><fr:anchor>3744</fr:anchor><fr:addr>jms-00MC</fr:addr><fr:route>jms-00MC.xml</fr:route><fr:title>Projection functions and <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00M8.xml"
addr="jms-00M8"
title="Surjection">surjections</fr:link></fr:title><fr:taxon>Example</fr:taxon><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>1</fr:month><fr:day>29</fr:day></fr:date><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link
type="local"
href="jonmsterling.xml"
addr="jonmsterling"
title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author><fr:contributor><fr:link
type="local"
href="marcelofiore.xml"
addr="marcelofiore"
title="Marcelo Fiore">Marcelo Fiore</fr:link></fr:contributor></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>The projection function <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\pi _1\colon  A\times  B\to  A]]></fr:tex> sending <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (a,b\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> to <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00M8.xml"
addr="jms-00M8"
title="Surjection">surjective</fr:link> if and only if either <html:span
xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[B \not =\varnothing ]]></fr:tex></html:span> or <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A=\varnothing ]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree
toc="false"
numbered="true"
show-heading="true"
show-metadata="false"
expanded="true"
root="false"
xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml"><fr:frontmatter><fr:anchor>3748</fr:anchor><fr:addr>#377</fr:addr><fr:route>unstable-377.xml</fr:route><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>1</fr:month><fr:day>29</fr:day></fr:date><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link
type="local"
href="jonmsterling.xml"
addr="jonmsterling"
title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:parent>jms-00MC</fr:parent></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>Suppose that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\pi _1\colon  A\times  B\to  A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00M8.xml"
addr="jms-00M8"
title="Surjection">surjective</fr:link>. We proceed by cases on whether <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is empty:</fr:p>
 <fr:ol><fr:li>If <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is empty, we are done.</fr:li>
  <fr:li>If <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is inhabited by some <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A]]></fr:tex>, then by assumption there exists <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[u\in  A\times  B]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\pi _1{\mathopen {}\left (u\right )\mathclose {}}=a]]></fr:tex>. Thus <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> is inhabited by <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\pi _2{\mathopen {}\left (u\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:li></fr:ol>

 <fr:p>Conversely, suppose that either <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[B\not =\varnothing ]]></fr:tex> or <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A=\varnothing ]]></fr:tex>. Fixing <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A]]></fr:tex>, we must show that there exists <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[u\in  A\times  B]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\pi _1{\mathopen {}\left (u\right )\mathclose {}}=a]]></fr:tex>. If <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A=\varnothing ]]></fr:tex>, then we have a contradiction already; on the other hand, if there exists any <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[b\in  B]]></fr:tex>, we may define <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[u:={\mathopen {}\left (a,b\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> and we are done.</fr:p>
</fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree>
 
</fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
